<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1295] Move javascript client from contrib to clients dir in source</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1295</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems odd that the javascript client is in the contrib, unless you think of it more of a library that you then hack up.  At any rate, here is the patch assuming you have done svn mv &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/trunk/contrib/javascript&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/trunk/contrib/javascript&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/trunk/client/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/trunk/client/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
